					<span class="category"><a href="http://ideas.ted.com/category/we-humans/" rel="category tag">We humans</a></span>

					<h1 class="single-post-title">Why I taught myself 20 languages &#8212; and what I learned about myself in the process</h1>
					<span class="date">Apr 9, 2015</span>


											<span class="separator"> / </span>
													<a href="http://ideas.ted.com/author/timothy-doner/" title="Posts by Timothy Doner" class="author url fn" rel="author">Timothy Doner</a>						
				</div>
				<!-- .article-header -->

				<div class="article-sharing">
					<div class="sharing-container">


